# Source files check out LF everywhere — with a global core.autocrlf=true,
# fresh checkouts smudged `.mjs` to CRLF and vite-node chokes on a
# shebang followed by CRLF (scripts/fidelity-tripwire.mjs broke inside
# vitest in BOTH the M7 and M8 worktrees). `text=auto` still auto-detects
# binaries, so images/fonts stay untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Vendored variant prototypes must stay BYTE-IDENTICAL to
# atlas-design-gallery/src/_prototype — the design canon cites them by
# file:line. No EOL normalization, ever. (Last match wins — this rule
# must stay below the `*` rule.)
design/variants/** -text
